    "This collaboration directly addresses the core weaknesses of each method.",
    "For instance, symbolic execution tools like KLEE encounter difficulties when dealing with external system interactions or code requiring domain knowledge (e.g., valid IP address formats).",
    "In contrast, LLMs excel in these areas.",
    "A comparative study [72] reveals that while KLEE fails in tasks involving parallel programming communication, ChatGPT can generate valid inputs.",
    "The hybrid framework LLMSym [139] puts this synergy into practice."
